      "updated": 1782540903132,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirments\n- users should be able to create group chats\n- users should be able to send the messages\n- when users are offline should receive the messages(below 30 days)\n- user should be able to send media/files\n\nNFR\n- should receive messages with low latency(<500ms)\n- should handle billions of users\n- gaurantee delivery of messages\n\nEntites\n- chat\n- chatParticipant\n- Message\n- Inbox\n\n commands sent\n- create chat\n- send message\n- create attachment\n\nCommands Recieved\n- new message\n- update / edit a message\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirments\n- users should be able to create group chats\n- users should be able to send the messages\n- when users are offline should receive the messages(below 30 days)\n- user should be able to send media/files\n\nNFR\n- should receive messages with low latency(<500ms)\n- should handle billions of users\n- gaurantee delivery of messages\n\nEntites\n- chat\n- chatParticipant\n- Message\n- Inbox\n\n commands sent\n- create chat\n- send message\n- create attachment\n\nCommands Recieved\n- new message\n- update / edit a message\n",
