      "text": "Client A sends Message\nClient b and C should recieve the meesage",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Client A sends Message\nClient b and C should recieve the meesage",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "d62eRjRHzib5Nd7U9kh0o",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1192.1821270462294,
      "y": 1993.7814470061492,
      "width": 903.6793823242188,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ab",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 935640027,
      "version": 532,
      "versionNonce": 1587144277,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782545367945,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. clent sends a message\n2. chat server looks up for all the participants from the chat partcipant table\n3. Chat server get the lits of partcipants -> [A, B, C]\n4. Producer removes the reciever and sends the message to the topic B, topic C \n5.  A, B, C is group chat so chat server1 send the message to target consumer b & C topics\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. clent sends a message\n2. chat server looks up for all the participants from the chat partcipant table\n3. Chat server get the lits of partcipants -> [A, B, C]\n4. Producer removes the reciever and sends the message to the topic B, topic C \n5.  A, B, C is group chat so chat server1 send the message to target consumer b & C topics\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
